name: Amundi Multi-Asset Portfolio UCITS ETF Dist
description_en: The Amundi Multi-Asset Portfolio UCITS ETF Dist is an actively managed ETF. The umbrella fund Amundi Multi-Asset Portfolio invests in various ETFs. The composition follows fixed allocation rules and is not actively managed. The strategy provides access to a globally diversified equity/bond/commodity portfolio. The weighting is reset once a year to the initial allocation of 60%/30%/10%. The ETF's TER (total expense ratio) amounts to 0.42% p.a.. The dividends in the ETF are distributed to the investors (Annually). The Amundi Multi-Asset Portfolio UCITS ETF Dist has 211m Euro assets under management. The ETF was launched on 12 April 2016 and is domiciled in Germany.

Vážení se resetuje jednou ročně na počáteční přidělení 60%/30%/10%. TER (poměr celkových nákladů) činí 0,42% p.a. dividenday v ETF jsou distribuovány investorům (každoročně).
